{"tha-ap478:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap478:0.2":"Nalamalivagga ","tha-ap478:0.3":"Kusatthakadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap478:1.1":"“Kassapassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap478:1.2":"brahmanassa vusimato; ","tha-ap478:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap478:1.4":"kusatthakamadasaham. ","tha-ap478:2.1":"Imasmimyeva kappasmim, ","tha-ap478:2.2":"kusatthakamadasaham; ","tha-ap478:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap478:2.4":"kusatthakassidam phalam. ","tha-ap478:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap478:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap478:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap478:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap478:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap478:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap478:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap478:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap478:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap478:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kusatthakadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap478:7.1":"Kusatthakadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}